Encoding considerations : binary


Security considerations : 
Messages contain no executable code nor URLs and are fully verified against static schema at the destination endpoint. Some private information may be exposed if message is not protected by the secure channel (e.g. TLS).

Interoperability considerations : 
The message interoperability is tested across all popular gaming platforms (Apple iOS, Apple OSX, Android, MS Windows, MS Windows Phone) and architectures (Intel, Arm).

Published specification : 
No published specification is available.

http://www.ea.com/real-racing-3/
http://www.ea.com/thesimsfreeplay/
http://www.ea.com/needforspeednolimits/
